# Tests, Inspections And Checks## Fire Alarm### Role
**Responsible:** Maintenance### Monthly
Every month the following test shall be conducted and if a fault is established, appropriate corrective action shall be taken:1. One manual alarm initiating device shall be operated, on a rotating basis, and shall initiate an alarm condition;

2. Function of all signal devices shall be ensured;
